'''谢默斯·科尔曼'''（{{lang-en|'''Séamus Coleman'''}}，{{bd|1988年|10月11日|catidx=Coleman, Séamus}}）是一名[[愛爾蘭|愛爾蘭]][[足球|足球]][[運動員|運動員]]，司職[[後衛_(足球)|右閘]]或[[中場|右中場]]，現時效力[[英超|英超]]球會[[埃弗顿足球俱乐部|愛華頓]]並擔任隊長。同時是[[愛爾蘭國家足球隊|愛爾蘭國家足球隊]]的隊長。

== 生平 ==
=== 球會 ===
;斯萊戈
高文在為家鄉球隊「启利贝格斯圣凯瑟琳」（St. Catherine's of Killybegs）[[友誼賽|友賽]][[斯萊戈流浪者足球俱樂部|斯萊戈]]（Sligo Rovers）時被對方發掘<ref>{{cite web |language=en |url=http://walkthechalk.com/player.php?id=1332 |title=Seamus Coleman |publisher=''Walk the chalk'' |accessdate=6 December 2009 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151222130127/http://walkthechalk.com/player.php?id=1332 |archive-date=2015-12-22 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，他於2006年10月14日主場對[[Waterford_United_F.C.|沃特福德联]]（Waterford United）處子上陣<ref>{{cite web |language=en |url=http://www.extratime.ie/newsdesk/articles/1209/ |title=Coleman completes Everton move |last=Davey |first=Christopher |date=1 February 2009 |publisher=''ExtraTime.ie'' |accessdate=6 December 2009 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090624130315/http://extratime.ie/newsdesk/articles/1209/ |archivedate=2009年6月24日 }}</ref>；並於2008年5月對[[布雷流浪者足球俱樂部|布雷流浪]]（Bray Wanderers）取得效力期間唯一入球<ref>{{cite web |language=en |url=http://www.rte.ie/sport/soccer/2008/0517/sligo_bray.html?rss |title=Sligo Rovers 3–0 Bray Wanderers |date=17 May 2008 |publisher=''[[RTE|RTE]]'' |accessdate=5 January 2010}}</ref>。

;愛華頓
[[埃弗顿足球俱乐部|愛華頓]]領隊[[大衛·莫耶斯|大衛·莫耶斯]]獲得前隊友[[Willie_McStay_(footballer_born_1961)|威利·麥史地]]（Willie McStay）的推薦，於2009年1月擊退[[伊普斯维奇城足球俱乐部|-{zh-hans:伊普斯维奇; zh-hk:葉士域治;}-]]、[[伯明翰足球會|伯明翰城]]及[[凯尔特人足球俱乐部|-{zh-hans:凯尔特人; zh-hk:些路迪;}-]]等表示有興趣的對手，以6萬[[英鎊|英鎊]]簽入高文<ref>{{cite web |language=en |url=http://www.people.co.uk/sport/tm_headline=hotline-everton-go-to-sea&method=full&objectid=21050827&siteid=93463-name_page.html |title=Everton to sign Seamus Coleman |date=19 January 2009 |publisher=''people.co.uk'' |accessdate=6 December 2009 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/68rWz1feO?url=http://www.people.co.uk/sport/tm_headline=hotline-everton-go-to-sea |archive-date=2012-07-02 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。尚未為「拖肥糖」上過陣，高文在夏季腳部感染生水泡，於季前[[美國|美國]]之旅甫抵達[[西雅圖|西雅圖]]即接受強力[[抗生素|抗生素]]治療，其後更需動[[手術|手術]]才挽救回其剛起步的足球事業<ref>{{cite web |language=en |url=http://soccernet.espn.go.com/news/story?id=683662&cc=5739 |title=New blow as James Vaughan undergoes surgery |date=7 October 2009 |publisher=''ESPN Soccernet'' |accessdate=6 December 2009 |archive-date=2012-10-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121024065916/http://soccernet.espn.go.com/news/story?id=683662&cc=5739 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。高文在[[2009/10賽季歐洲聯賽#分組賽|歐霸盃分組賽]]作客0-5大敗於[[本菲卡足球俱樂部|-{zh-hans:本菲卡; zh-hk:賓菲加;}-]]腳下首次代表愛華頓上陣<ref>{{cite web |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/europe/8318447.stm |title=Benfica 5–0 Everton |last=Brett |first=Oliver |date=22 October 2009 |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |accessdate=6 December 2009 |archive-date=2016-01-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160112221824/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/europe/8318447.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>；三天後首次在[[英超|英超]]上陣，作客2-3不敵[[博尔顿足球俱乐部|保頓]]，於賽事末段後補入替[[约翰·海廷加|-{zh-hans:海廷加;zh-hk:希丁加;}-]]<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/8316289.stm |title=Bolton 3-2 Everton |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2009-10-25 |accessdate=2010-12-06 |archive-date=2009-10-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091028102124/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/8316289.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>；而主場處子戰則在[[英超|英超]]迎戰[[托特纳姆热刺足球俱乐部|熱刺]]，上半場15分鐘後補入替賽前已有傷在身的[[約瑟·尤保|尤保]]，高文登場後整條防線四人全由[[後衛_(足球)#邊後衛|二閘]]球員組成，[[托尼·希伯特|-{zh-hans:希伯特; zh-hk:希拔;}-]]移中與[[盧卡斯·尼爾|尼爾]]鎮守中路，[[莱顿·拜恩斯|拜恩斯]]與高文分任左、右閘，雖然先失兩球，但一對二閘各貢獻一個助攻，協助球隊扳平2-2完場<ref>{{cite web |language=en |url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/football/2009/dec/06/premier-league-everton-tottenham-hotspur |title=Tim Howard's injury-time penalty save caps gallant Everton fightback |last=Hunter |first=Andy |date=6 December 2009 |publisher=''guardian.co.uk'' |accessdate=6 December 2009 |archive-date=2009-12-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091209021223/http://www.guardian.co.uk/football/2009/dec/06/premier-league-everton-tottenham-hotspur |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2010年3月高文獲外借到[[英冠|英冠]]球會[[黑池足球會|黑池]]，初步為期1個月<ref>{{cite web |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/b/blackpool/8576974.stm |title=Blackpool sign Everton full-back Seamus Coleman on loan |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2010-03-19 |accessdate=2010-03-24 |archive-date=2012-07-02 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/68rX03owZ?url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/b/blackpool/8576974.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，於主場2-2賽和[[水晶宫足球俱乐部|水晶宮]]首度披甲<ref>{{cite web |language=en |url=http://www.mirrorfootball.co.uk/news/Blackpool-2-2-Crystal-Palace-Last-gasp-Ben-Burgess-plunges-Palace-into-the-drop-zone-The-Sunday-Mirror-match-report-article362013.html |title=Blackpool 2–2 Crystal Palace |publisher=''The Sunday Mirror'' |date=201–03–20 |accessdate=2010-03-24 |archive-date=2012-10-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121014235827/http://www.mirrorfootball.co.uk/news/Blackpool-2-2-Crystal-Palace-Last-gasp-Ben-Burgess-plunges-Palace-into-the-drop-zone-The-Sunday-Mirror-match-report-article362013.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>；並在作客4-2擊敗[[斯坎索普联足球俱乐部|-{zh-hans:斯坎索普; zh-hk:斯肯索普;}-]]為「橙衣軍團」（''the Tangerines''）射入1球<ref>{{cite web |language=en |url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/football/article-1263130/Scunthorpe-2-Blackpool-4-DJ-Campbell-double-Ian-Holloways-troops.html |title=Scunthorpe 2 Blackpool 4: DJ Campbell at the double as Ian Holloway's troops march towards the play-offs |first=Alan |last=Biggs |publisher=''The Daily Mail'' |date=2010-04-02 |accessdate=2010-04-06 |archive-date=2010-04-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100406224526/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/football/article-1263130/Scunthorpe-2-Blackpool-4-DJ-Campbell-double-Ian-Holloways-troops.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。到4月，他的借用合約獲延長至球季結束<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11095_6094501,00.html |title=Coleman sticks with Blackpool |publisher=''Sky Sports'' |date=2010-04-15 |accessdate=2010-12-06 |archive-date=2012-07-02 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/68rX1Faf4?url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11095_6094501,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，外借期間高文同意與愛華頓續約四年<ref>{{cite web |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/e/everton/8692668.stm |title=Defender Seamus Coleman signs new deal at Everton |date=2010-05-19 |work=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |accessdate=2010-05-19 |archive-date=2010-05-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100521135207/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/e/everton/8692668.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，而黑池則在聯賽取得第6位及參加升班附加賽的資格，高文出席所有3場附加賽，先於準決賽兩回合累計6-4淘汰[[诺丁汉森林足球俱乐部|-{zh-hans:诺丁汉森林;zh-hk:諾定咸森林;}-]]，決賽於5月22日在[[溫布萊球場|溫布萊球場]]迎戰[[卡迪夫城足球俱乐部|卡迪夫城]]，黑池以3-2僅勝取得來季升班[[英超|英超]]最後一個席位<ref name="Blackpool 3-2 Cardiff City">{{cite news | language = en | title = Blackpool 3-2 Cardiff City | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_div_1/8692465.stm | publisher = ''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' | date = 2010-05-22 | accessdate = 2010-05-22 | archive-date = 2012-03-30 | archive-url = https://www.webcitation.org/66XYsASwg?url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/8692465.stm | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

2010年9月21日高文於[[英格蘭聯賽盃|英格蘭聯賽盃]]第三圈作客對[[布伦特福德足球俱乐部|-{zh-hans:布伦特福德; zh-hk:賓福特;}-]]射入加盟愛華頓後首個入球<ref>{{cite web |language=en |url=http://www.mirrorfootball.co.uk/news/HT-Brentford-1-1-Everton-Seamus-Coleman-gets-his-first-Toffee-s-goal-but-Gary-Alexander-pegs-one-back-article585573.html |title=HT Brentford 1-1 Everton |publisher=''mirrorfootball.co.uk'' |date=2010-09-21 |accessdate=2010-10-14 |archive-date=2010-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100924145505/http://www.mirrorfootball.co.uk/news/HT-Brentford-1-1-Everton-Seamus-Coleman-gets-his-first-Toffee-s-goal-but-Gary-Alexander-pegs-one-back-article585573.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>；11月6日在[[英超|英超]]作客對上季末曾效力的[[黑池足球會|黑池]]，高文射入1球為愛華頓追平2-2終場<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/9149903.stm |title=Blackpool 2-2 Everton |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2010-11-06 |accessdate=2010-12-06 |archive-date=2010-11-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101111111856/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/9149903.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2012年12月31日，[[愛華頓|愛華頓]]宣佈與高文續約5年半至2018年夏季<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.evertonfc.com/news/archive/2012/12/31/coleman-signs-new-deal |title=Coleman Signs New Deal |publisher=evertonfc.com |date=2012-12-31 |accessdate=2012-12-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130103233509/http://www.evertonfc.com/news/archive/2012/12/31/coleman-signs-new-deal |archive-date=2013-01-03 |dead-url=yes }}</ref></small>。
高文奪得2013-14賽季愛華頓年度最佳球員。

===國家隊===
高文曾代表愛爾蘭U18學童隊，並協助球隊於2006年保留「百年盾」（Centenary Shield）。高文於2008年首次代表[[愛爾蘭21歲以下國家足球隊|愛爾蘭U21]]上陣出戰[[瑞典21歲以下國家足球隊|瑞典U21]]<ref>{{cite web |language=en |url=http://www.loi.ie/index.php/clubs/premier-division/galway-united/latest-news/430-oshea-helps-ireland-u21-to-victory |title=O'Shea helps Ireland U21 to victory | League of Ireland – Real Football, Real Fans |publisher=loi.ie |date= |accessdate=24 June 2009 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090401204804/http://www.loi.ie/index.php/clubs/premier-division/galway-united/latest-news/430-oshea-helps-ireland-u21-to-victory |archivedate=2009年4月1日 }}</ref><ref>
{{cite web |language=en |url=http://www.rte.ie/sport/soccer/2009/0316/ireland1.html|title=RTÉ Sport: Given announces 18-man U-21 squad |publisher=RTÉ |accessdate=24 June 2009 |date=16 March 2009}}</ref>。他於2010年10月首次獲徵召加入[[愛爾蘭國家足球隊|大國腳]]行列<ref>{{cite web |language=en |url=http://www.rte.ie/sport/soccer/2010/1001/ireland_colemans.html |title=RTÉ Sport: Seamus Coleman named in Trap's squad |date=1 October 2010 |publisher=RTÉ |accessdate=13 October 2010 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101002121025/http://www.rte.ie/sport/soccer/2010/1001/ireland_colemans.html |archivedate=2010-10-02 }}</ref>，並於2011年2月8日獲派首次上陣出戰[[威爾斯足球代表隊|威爾斯]]<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.rte.ie/sport/soccer/2011/0208/ireland_wales_carlingnationscup.html |title=Republic of Ireland 3-0 Wales |publisher=[[RTE|''rte.ie'']] |date=2011-02-08 |accessdate=2011-03-15 |archive-date=2011-02-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110211022530/http://www.rte.ie/sport/soccer/2011/0208/ireland_wales_carlingnationscup.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。
2016年9月，在罗比·基恩从国际上退役后，科尔曼被任命为爱尔兰永久队长。次月，在2018年世界杯预选赛中，他在阿维瓦体育场1-0战胜格鲁吉亚的比赛中为爱尔兰打进了他的第一个高级国际进球。

